<h1>Battle Reports at Leeds Night Owls</h1>
<p>A few of the more notable games played at Night Owls that members have been kind enough to write up to give a flavour for the tabletop wargaming we do at the club.</p>

{% for report in collections['battle-report'] | reverse %}
<div class="row mb-4 border-bottom pb-4">
  <div class="col-md-4">
    <a href="{{ report.url }}">
      <img src="{{ report.data.thumbnail }}" alt="{{ report.data.thumbnailAlt }}" class="img-fluid rounded" style="max-height: 220px; width: 100%; object-fit: cover;">
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-8">
    <h2><a href="{{ report.url }}" class="text-decoration-none">{{ report.data.title }}</a></h2>
    <p class="text-muted">{{ report.date | readableDate }}</p>
    {% if report.data.description %}<p>{{ report.data.description }}</p>{% endif %}
    <a href="{{ report.url }}" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm">Read report</a>
  </div>
</div>
{% endfor %}
